{
  "info": {
    "name": "Sotang API",
    "description": "Colección MVP — Auth · Accounts · Categories · Budgets · Goals\n\n## Setup\n1. Importa también el **environment** `Sotang_Local.postman_environment.json`.\n2. Ejecuta **Auth / Register** o **Auth / Login** — el `accessToken` y `refreshToken` se guardan automáticamente en el environment.\n3. Todos los endpoints autenticados usan `{{accessToken}}` en el header `Authorization`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "event": [],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Registro, login, refresh y logout. Login y Register guardan el token automáticamente.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const res = pm.response.json();",
                "if (res.accessToken) {",
                "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  res.accessToken);",
                "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                "  pm.environment.set('userId',       res.user.id);",
                "  console.log('✅ Tokens guardados. userId:', res.user.id);",
                "}"
              ]
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nombre\": \"Jefferson Palma\",\n  \"email\": \"jeff@sotang.app\",\n  \"password\": \"miPassword123\",\n  \"timezone\": \"America/Guayaquil\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Crea un usuario nuevo y devuelve accessToken (15 min) + refreshToken (30 días)."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const res = pm.response.json();",
                "if (res.accessToken) {",
                "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  res.accessToken);",
                "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                "  pm.environment.set('userId',       res.user.id);",
                "  console.log('✅ Tokens guardados. userId:', res.user.id);",
                "}"
              ]
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"jeff@sotang.app\",\n  \"password\": \"miPassword123\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Autentica al usuario. Los tokens se guardan automáticamente en el environment."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [{
            "listen": "test",
            "script": {
              "exec": [
                "const res = pm.response.json();",
                "if (res.accessToken) {",
                "  pm.environment.set('accessToken',  res.accessToken);",
                "  pm.environment.set('refreshToken', res.refreshToken);",
                "  console.log('✅ Token renovado');",
                "}"
              ]
            }
          }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","refresh"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Rota el refreshToken y emite un nuevo accessToken. El token anterior queda revocado."
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{accessToken}}", "type": "string" }] },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api","v1","auth","logout"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Revoca el refreshToken. Requiere accessToken en el header."
          }
        }

      ]
    },

